ca.weblite.objc
Interface Runtime

All Superinterfaces:
com.sun.jna.Library
public interface Runtime
extends com.sun.jna.Library

A JNA wrapper around the objective-c runtime. This contains all of the functions needed to interact with the runtime (e.g. send messages, etc..).

Sample Usage
